2k04 A 11 C 265

A redox-regulated disulphide may form between two units of Stromal cell-derived factor 1 at these cysteines. However, the redox score of this cysteine pair is lower than any known redox-active disulphide.

Stromal cell-derived factor 1

4lmq F 34 F 50
